snippet.title: Wolf Gang Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a band of wolves as they take control of the mountain using turn based tactical combat in a humorous adventure campaign! Get the demo to Wolf Gang and support the development of the project on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nylonblonde/wolf-gang-a-tactical-rpg-with-a-twist

Follow us on twitter or facebook for more news and updates!
https://twitter.com/nylon_blonde
https://www.facebook.com/nylonblonde/
